<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-02-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-02-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="899" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d899">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 855.48/483</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Netherland Minister</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_RCWLFC1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Van
                                Rappard</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <p rend="center">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Confirmation</hi>
                        </p>
                        <p>The Netherland Minister presents his compliments to his excellency the
                            Secretary of State and begs leave to bring to the latter’s <pb facs="0810" n="638" xml:id="pg_638"/> notice that in case the
                            American citizens now engaged in the relief work in Belgium would be
                            compelled by the circumstances to leave that country, the Netherland
                            Government would be glad to form a committee of Dutch subjects who would
                            work under its patronage and take over, either alone or in concerted
                            action with other neutrals, the duties till now performed by the
                            American commission.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <dateline rendition="#left">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                                </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-02-14"><hi rend="italic">14 February 1917</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>